s and support services  advanced programs inc capabilities and support services as the global leader in tempest products and services apis capabilities and proficiencies are rooted in our forty  plus years of tempest market focus apis exceptionally qualified work force is committed to fulfilling apis mission and maintaining industry leading quality as an nsa certified tempest engineering manufacturing and iso  compliant small business api maintains a level of commitment to engineer build deliver and support solutions and services that meet our clients highest security and quality standards from life cycle support to training services api maintains a comprehensive suite of services and capabilities that ensure the best quality products are being produced by the most qualified personnel read below to learn more about our various capabilities rfi engineering and system design services api engineers and designs it products and systems to resolve radio frequency interference rfi concerns as well as to withstand adverse conditions this supports the physical layer of information assurance that is required by many of our government and defense customers apis innovative tempestemi and other engineering and system design services meet security and quality compliance standards  establish a base of trust and is the cornerstone for the success of apis products and solutions api offers government agencies and system integrators who are developing and designing products to meet defense and custom product functionality access to our engineering and design expertise as a service either as joint partnerships or contracted tasks api mechanical electrical cyber system and tempest engineers are available to assist client design and build products and solutions compliant with tempest emi or ruggedization standards engineering practices such as d modeling crossfunction critical design review teams and rapid prototype development allows api to offer responsive support adaptable to the inevitable compressed product design schedule additionally apis extensive tempestemimilstd testing resources allows api as part of the development process to prescan products to validate design integrity life cycle support for over  years api has offered full life cycle support on the products we manufacture supporting fieldsite deployments for military and intelligence community missions worldwide this support includes configuration management documentation training installation depot repair break fix maintenance support and issue tracking a dedicated customer service team support in coordination with geographically disbursed field personnel to deliver rapid and responsive support api specialized repair and warranty agreements cover repair services performed in europe and australia repair service performed in secure facilities by cleared personnel shock vibration heat etc onsite repairs extended warranties staging of spare equipment and parts configuration control tracking and management contact api customer service team toll free at advprog  or  or email us at serviceadvprogramscom to learn more about our life cycle services assembly and manufacturing api strives for get it right the first time production performance a comprehensive testing strategy conducts incoming component inspections workinprogress inspection and thorough verification and validation for prototypes as well as statistically appropriate level of production sampling types of testing include functional stress thermal tempest and emi apis formal scalable assembly processes with fully integrated quality checks from material sourcing to finished goods shipment delivers repeatable high quality production and product integrity essential for market success with over  square feet of production space at our columbia md and salem nh facilities api has the capacity and flexibility to address a variety of production needs appropriate facility clearances and a us citizen only work force also allows us to also support classified product production training api provides formal training courses on the maintenance and repair of api tempest products for most clients we offer self directed training materials on line at no charge to provide user training customers attending an api training class learn the proper disassembly and reassembly techniques for a particular product or group of products reporting requirements and the techniques to ensure that tempest systems integrity is not compromised as they repair or preventative maintenance functions are preformed with completion attendees receive a certificate of completion an identification code and access to our support website for technical data configuration and log management of their devices training sessions are available at api offices or customer sites the tempest compliance of all equipment manufactured by advanced programs inc is guaranteed for the life of the product when repairs are performed by api staff or technicians or clients who have attended appropriate api training and been certified course customization is available for unique solutions and trainthetrainer needs please note that international customers may be required to have a technical assistance agreement taa approved before api can provide technical training to arrange for training please contact the api training team at  or trainingadvprogramscom serving the united states  all nato countries l advanced programs inc  government contractor vvfubbzxecvbcxbr government contracts federal agencies more  search government contractors × menu see all government contractors overviewcontractscategoriesproductsservicesplace of performancevendor details l advanced programs inc overviewcontractscategoriesproductsservicesmoreplace of performancevendor details l advanced programs inc overview contracts categories productsservices place of performance vendor details references see all government contractors research guide share l advanced programs inc government contractor 